            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#咽喉炎高发季如何减少刀片嗓#】#咽喉炎三分治七分养# 受气温降低、空气变干燥、植物花粉浓度增加等因素的影响，秋天是咽喉炎高发季。针对“吞刀片”般...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%92%BD%E5%96%89%E7%82%8E%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%91%E5%AD%A3%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%88%80%E7%89%87%E5%97%93%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%92%BD%E5%96%89%E7%82%8E%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%91%E5%AD%A3%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%88%80%E7%89%87%E5%97%93%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#咽喉炎高发季如何减少刀片嗓#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%92%BD%E5%96%89%E7%82%8E%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%83%E5%88%86%E5%85%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%92%BD%E5%96%89%E7%82%8E%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%83%E5%88%86%E5%85%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#咽喉炎三分治七分养#</span></a> 受气温降低、空气变干燥、植物花粉浓度增加等因素的影响，秋天是咽喉炎高发季。针对“吞刀片”般的急性咽喉痛，可服用止痛药。⚠️还要注意：①尽量吃温热的东西，多饮水，避免辛辣刺激性食物；②可使用加湿器或新风系统，改善环境湿度，减少空气中飘散的刺激物；③注意保暖👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4954835762479120" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hioo5a93lkj60hg0n9ap302.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/8IJwPOHhlx089eo8uQUo01041200xjrc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696828462&amp;ssig=T153q1caF6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nAilVN42lx089eo9h9Ne01041200jueh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696828462&amp;ssig=CVMHfJPUmG&amp;KID=u