            <description><![CDATA[【⚠️注意预防！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%BA%A62.45%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E6%82%A3%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%BA%A62.45%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E6%82%A3%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国约2.45亿人患高血压#</span></a>】有数据显示，我国大约每4个成年人中就有1人是高血压患者，患病人数约2.45亿。有家族史、情绪易激动、摄盐量偏高等人群，为高血压易发人群。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提示：如果经常出现头部胀痛、阵发性眩晕、胸闷不适、四肢麻木等症状，应及时进行血压监测，警惕是不是早期高血压的信号。 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4954489157779504" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hinkevhyzjj61pq0yq4qp02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nsaTSAw6lx089cRHDq5201041200XJJW0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=1696828476&amp;ssig=8PR%2F3B%2BHM%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/y0Ac04kalx089cRGWGI001041200v2Av0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=1696828476&amp;ssig=QipG1kiBNF&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5JJgQKnTlx089cRGKPRS01041200jUcG0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=6